SourceCode_List.SourceCode:
public class Pet { 

static int count ; 

String pid ; 

String name ; 

String type ; 

Pet ( String t , String p , String n ) { 

type = t ; 

name = n ; 

pid = p ; 

} 

void speak ( ) { 

if ( type == "狗" ) System . out . println ( "您的寵物叫聲是：汪汪\r\n" ) ; 

else System . out . println ( "您的寵物叫聲是：喵喵\r\n" ) ; 

} 

public void display ( ) { 

System . out . println ( "寵物種類：" + type ) ; 

System . out . println ( "寵物編號：" + pid ) ; 

System . out . println ( "寵物名稱：" + name ) ; 

} 

}

public class Keeper
{
    String Id;
    String Tel;
    Keeper(String i,String t)
    {
        Id=i;
        Tel=t;
    }
    public void display()
    {
        System.out.println("飼主身分證字號："+Id);
        System.out.println("飼主電話："+Tel);
    }
}

import java.util.Scanner;
public class shop
{
    public static void main(String[] args)
    {
        System.out.println("請輸入寵物種類：");
        System.out.println("請輸入寵物編號：");
        System.out.println("請輸入寵物名稱：");
        System.out.println("請輸入飼主身分證字號：");
        System.out.println("請輸入飼主電話：");

        Pet p=new Pet(args[0],args[1],args[2]);
        Keeper user=new Keeper(args[3],args[4]);

        p.display();
        user.display();
        p.speak();
    }
}

Error.Message:
Pet物件類需要有一個物件資料，類型是Keeper以表示
Pet物件的Keeper是誰。
可在第5行下加入private Keeper keeper;
並且在Pet ( String t , String p , String n )的括弧裡加入 Keeper keeper;
